      "len": 67,
      "en": "$N turns to $Y. \"It'll cost you #4 gold for the deed. Interested?\" ",
      "zh": "$N 轉向 $Y。「船契需 #4 枚金幣。汝有意嗎？」",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "offset": 1207,
      "len": 33,
      "en": "\"You look pretty full to me, $Y.\"",
      "zh": "「汝看起來行李很滿，$Y。」",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "offset": 1321,
      "len": 60,
